Package: minecraft-python-server
Version: 1.0.0
Section: games
Priority: optional
Architecture: __ARCH__
Depends: libc6
Maintainer: ronit-mishra-04 <ronit-mishra-04@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Minecraft Server Installer & Control Panel
 A complete solution for installing and managing Minecraft servers on Ubuntu.
 Includes server setup (Vanilla, Paper, Spigot), Java auto-installation
 via Azul Zulu, and a terminal-based control panel for starting/stopping servers.
 .
 Commands provided:
   minecraft-server          - Install and set up a Minecraft server
   minecraft-server-ui       - Control panel to start/stop your server
   minecraft-server-uninstall - Remove installed servers and Java
